HEADWORD: Pomace
<hw>Pom"ace</hw> <pr>(?; 277)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>ponum</ets> a fruit, LL., an apple: cf. LL. <ets>pomagium</ets>,
